Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.03,0:00:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不久之後天神即將降臨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.31,0:00:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,人類這一種族或許要面臨極限了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.05,0:00:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我們有成為御姿的勇者大人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.90,0:00:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,假若能按計劃完成神婚儀式
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.38,0:00:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,從神樹大人那獲得新的力量的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.23,0:00:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,又得強迫她們經歷殘酷的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.13,0:00:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我們是無力的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.28,0:00:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,僅能側耳傾聽與誠心祈禱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.97,0:00:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,所謂勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.34,0:00:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,是被選中的人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.11,0:00:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,此乃至高的榮譽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.84,0:00:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有其他的辦法了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.71,0:00:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,為了保護神性低下的人民
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.37,0:00:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,這是最後的手段
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.05,0:00:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,大家化身一體
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.19,0:00:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我們將得到拯救
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.16,0:00:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,那種形態 究竟能被稱作是活著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.64,0:01:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你的話有點太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.06,0:01:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,此後的狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.91,0:01:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,已經不是僅為人類的我們能改變得了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.38,0:01:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,交託給勇者大人和神樹大人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.39,0:01:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,關於勇者大人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.92,0:01:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,她們是否會
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.95,0:01:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,妨礙儀式呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.02,0:01:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,如果變成那樣 再加上天神的攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.27,0:01:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,事態怕是會一發不可收拾
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.91,0:01:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,或許吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.61,0:01:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,倘若如此 我們就接受現實吧\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.41,0:01:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,這便是我們的宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.24,0:01:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,縱使人世終結
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.46,0:01:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,人的靈魂亦將與地神同在 永存
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.06,0:01:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,與神樹大人同在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.62,0:01:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,與神樹大人同在
Comment: 0,0:01:54.51,0:01:57.18,Title,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\k20}我{\k20}的{\k20}心{\k20}在{\k20}燃{\k20}燒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.51,0:02:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.80,0:02:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,勇者之魂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.85,0:03:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,知曉人類的力量了嗎 天神
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.09,0:03:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣 小鷲她們就能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.90,0:03:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,樹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.41,0:03:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,樹 現在的我只會拖後腿 放我下去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.78,0:03:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你在說什麼 夏凜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.03,0:03:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我決不允許這種事發生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.92,0:03:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我們要去和姐姐她們匯合
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.54,0:03:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,奪回友奈 帶上所有人一起回去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.63,0:03:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.47,0:04:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,東鄉 能做到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.58,0:04:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,一定可以
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.52,0:04:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.69,0:04:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,道路就由我來…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.07,0:04:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,開闢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.77,0:05:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,東鄉 拜託了 你一定要抵達
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.82,0:05:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,再這樣失去任何一個人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.33,0:05:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我都無法原諒自己
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.27,0:05:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我變成怎樣都無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.23,0:05:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,所以求求你 求你了 神明大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.03,0:05:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,樹…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.01,0:05:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,她沒事吧 一定要活著
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.65,0:05:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.48,0:05:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼是我們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.76,0:05:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼要帶走友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.45,0:05:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不幹壞事就無法存在的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.68,0:05:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,那種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.69,0:06:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我不承認是神
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.03,0:06:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我們犧牲了太多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.71,0:06:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,為國犧牲也是無可奈何
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.03,0:06:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信那是高尚且正確的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.33,0:07:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我深愛著這個國家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.69,0:07:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.49,0:07:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.63,0:07:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,這到底是什麼地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.57,0:07:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,憑藉精靈的力量能回得去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.15,0:07:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了 求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.35,0:07:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.74,0:07:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,東鄉 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.00,0:07:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,回去吧 友奈 我來接你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.21,0:08:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你們不惜這樣做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.65,0:08:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,也不願意將她交給我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.92,0:08:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈 我現在就來救你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.47,0:08:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 是我 必須是由我來做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.38,0:08:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不然世界就會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.05,0:08:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想要失去友奈你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.93,0:08:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼你不明白我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.29,0:08:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,必須由我來做 這只有我能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.40,0:08:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,這種事不做也罷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.32,0:08:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,真不像東鄉的風格
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.41,0:08:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,明明是最為國家著想的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.25,0:08:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,即使如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.03,0:08:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,這是必須有人來做 別無選擇的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.16,0:08:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼別無選擇 那種東西怎樣都好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.82,0:08:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想再被奪走重要的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.49,0:09:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝 東鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.04,0:09:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼又在說冠冕堂皇的的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.27,0:09:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼要一直忍耐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.31,0:09:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,因為只需要我一個人忍耐下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.61,0:09:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.10,0:09:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.25,0:09:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,說出你的真心話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.13,0:09:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,如果害怕就講出來 告訴我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.94,0:09:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,說你不想做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.46,0:09:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我們是朋友的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.31,0:09:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,就說救救我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.58,0:09:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.07,0:09:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我好怕 但是我不能說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.21,0:09:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,但這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.55,0:09:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想死
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.89,0:09:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想和大家分別啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.73,0:09:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.78,0:10:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我們明明已經這麼拚命了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.22,0:10:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,但是為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.91,0:10:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,因為是使命所以無可奈何什麼的都是騙人的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.14,0:10:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,永遠 永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.19,0:10:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,想和大家永遠在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.89,0:10:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈 把手伸出來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.92,0:10:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,東鄉 救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.50,0:10:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.90,0:10:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,東鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.63,0:10:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼會 居然做到這種程度也要…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.33,0:11:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼會 居然做到這種程度也要…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.63,0:11:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,東鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.38,0:11:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,救…救我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.24,0:11:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.32,0:11:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,東…鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.56,0:11:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.75,0:11:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.59,0:11:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,這種事情 我們並沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.73,0:11:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然很感激 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.47,0:11:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 已經夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.63,0:12:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,捨棄人類的身份 捨棄朋友才能獲得的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.26,0:12:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.92,0:12:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.74,0:12:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.42,0:13:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,神樹大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.70,0:13:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,世上有各種各樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.57,0:13:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,即使如此 如果您真的想拯救人類
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.85,0:13:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,能否
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.92,0:13:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,相信人類呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.79,0:13:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.44,0:14:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,將沿著身為人類的道路前進
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.00,0:14:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.86,0:14:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,東鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.77,0:14:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.70,0:14:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,東鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.76,0:14:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,東鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.80,0:14:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起 對不起 我說過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.77,0:14:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我 我才應該道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.02,0:14:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,對大家 對東鄉講了過分的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.80,0:14:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係 沒關係了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.78,0:15:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼辦 世界 世界要終結了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.28,0:15:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,這不是友奈的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.94,0:15:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,如果世界就這樣終結
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.11,0:15:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,那也是無可奈何的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.27,0:15:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,牛鬼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.25,0:15:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你要幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.69,0:15:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.45,0:15:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,好溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.28,0:16:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.52,0:17:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我 我們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.28,0:17:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,將作為人類戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.03,0:17:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,想活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.44,0:17:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,勇者不屈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.27,0:17:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,無論幾次都能重振旗鼓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.86,0:17:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,上啊 友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.94,0:17:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,為了友奈的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.13,0:17:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,只要去做
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.84,0:17:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,總會有辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.55,0:17:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,勇者部
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.76,0:17:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.60,0:18:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,勇者就是靠毅力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.56,0:18:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,勇者拳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.85,0:19:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,火焰正在…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.18,0:19:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.99,0:19:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,和平常的不一樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.10,0:20:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,牛鬼你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.78,0:20:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.07,0:20:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,永別了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.46,0:20:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我們回來…了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.91,0:20:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,世界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.94,0:21:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,還好好的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.43,0:21:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,神樹大人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.95,0:21:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,消失了 散華…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.61,0:21:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,一如既往的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.53,0:21:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了友奈 身體不舒服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.77,0:21:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.73,0:21:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,烙印消失了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.59,0:21:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.83,0:21:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,大家 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.08,0:21:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我才是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.86,0:21:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.45,0:21:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,夏凜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.45,0:21:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎回來 友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.66,0:22:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我回來了
